### UserActivity API Test Requests

### Get all user activities
GET https://localhost:7000/UserActivity
Content-Type: application/json

### Get user activity by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/UserActivity/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get user activities by user ID
GET https://localhost:7000/UserActivity/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get user activities with filters
POST https://localhost:7000/UserActivity/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "activityType": "login",
  "fromDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "limit": 10,
  "offset": 0
}

### Create new user activity
POST https://localhost:7000/UserActivity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "activityType": "login",
  "activityDate": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
  "metadata": "{\"ipAddress\": \"192.168.1.1\", \"userAgent\": \"Mozilla/5.0...\", \"location\": \"Ho Chi Minh City\"}"
}

### Update user activity
PUT https://localhost:7000/UserActivity/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "activityType": "logout",
  "activityDate": "2024-01-15T11:30:00Z",
  "metadata": "{\"ipAddress\": \"192.168.1.1\", \"userAgent\": \"Mozilla/5.0...\", \"location\": \"Ho Chi Minh City\", \"sessionDuration\": 3600}"
}

### Delete user activity
DELETE https://localhost:7000/UserActivity/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create user activity with simple text (will be auto-converted to JSON)
POST https://localhost:7000/UserActivity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "activityType": "page_view",
  "activityDate": "2024-01-15T12:00:00Z",
  "metadata": "User visited homepage"
}

### Create user activity with valid JSON
POST https://localhost:7000/UserActivity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "activityType": "search",
  "activityDate": "2024-01-15T12:30:00Z",
  "metadata": "{\"query\": \"hotels in Da Nang\", \"filters\": {\"price\": \"100-500\", \"rating\": 4}, \"results\": 15}"
}
